sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Player
participant QuizConsole
participant QuizRepository
participant QuizService
participant QuizJson as "quiz.json"


QuizConsole->>QuizRepository: loadQuestions()
alt quiz.json exists
  QuizRepository->>QuizJson: read questions array
  QuizJson-->>QuizRepository: question records
  QuizRepository-->>QuizConsole: vector<Question>
else file missing
  QuizRepository-->>QuizConsole: empty question set
end
QuizConsole->>QuizService: setQuestions(questions)
QuizService-->>QuizConsole: system ready
QuizConsole-->>Player: Display menu(Start Quiz, View Last Score, Exit)
